  </subsection>
  <subsection>
    <title>Graphs of Polynomials</title>
    <p>So far, we have considered the terminology of polynomials and how to combine them with addition, subtraction and multiplication.  Now let us consider them as functions. What does the graph of a polynomial look like? Here are a few examples:</p>
